Let me compile the comprehensive integration architecture report based on my research:

---

# Integration Architecture for Unified CRM/Project Management System

**Research Question:**
How can NocoDB, Planka, Metabase, n8n, and Ntfy be integrated to create a unified CRM/Project Management system similar to Monday.com?

**Date:** 2026-01-31  
**System Environment:**
- NocoDB: http://localhost:8080 (SQLite backend at `/mnt/c/Users/password/Documents/.claude/docker/nocodb/noco.db`)
- Planka: http://localhost:3000 (PostgreSQL backend at planka-db)
- Metabase: http://localhost:3001 (PostgreSQL metadata DB)
- n8n: http://localhost:5678
- Ntfy: http://localhost:8095

---

## 1. NocoDB Webhook/API Capabilities

### Authentication
- **API Token**: Use `xc-token` header for authentication
- **JWT Secret**: Configured as `NC_AUTH_JWT_SECRET=claude-nocodb-secret-change-me`
- **Token Generation**: Via Admin Settings > API Tokens

### Webhook v3 (2026) - Latest Version

**Event Types:**
- `after insert` - Triggers when records are created (single or bulk)
- `after update` - Triggers when records are updated (single or bulk)
- `after delete` - Triggers when records are deleted (single or bulk)

**Advanced Triggers:**
- **Send Everything** - Single configuration to capture all changes (Insert, Update, Delete)
- **Field-level triggers** - Fire webhooks only when specific fields change (e.g., Status, Priority)
- **View-based triggers** - When views are created, updated, or deleted
- **Manual triggers** - User-initiated via webhook button

**Webhook Payload Structure (v3):**
```json
{
  "type": "records.after.insert",
  "id": "9dac1c54-b3be-49a1-a676-af388145fa8c",
  "data": {
    "table_id": "md_xzru7dcqrecc60",
    "table_name": "Film",
    "view_id": "vw_736wrpoas7tr0c",
    "view_name": "Film",
    "records": [
      {
        "FilmId": 1011,
        "Title": "FOO",
        "Language": {
          "LanguageId": 1,
          "Name": "English"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

**For Update Events:**
```json
{
  "type": "records.after.update",
  "data": {
    "table_id": "...",
    "table_name": "...",
    "records": [...],
    "previous_rows": [...]  // Contains data before update
  }
}
```

### REST API v3 (Beta)

**Base URL Pattern:** `http://localhost:8080/api/v3/{projectId}/...`

**Key Endpoints:**
- `GET /api/v3/projects` - List all projects
- `GET /api/v3/projects/{projectId}/tables` - List tables in project
- `POST /api/v3/projects/{projectId}/tables/{tableId}/records` - Create record
- `GET /api/v3/projects/{projectId}/tables/{tableId}/records` - List records
- `PATCH /api/v3/projects/{projectId}/tables/{tableId}/records/{recordId}` - Update record
- `DELETE /api/v3/projects/{projectId}/tables/{tableId}/records/{recordId}` - Delete record

**Webhook Actions Available:**
- **HTTP Request**: GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, PATCH, HEAD with custom headers/body
- **Run Script**: Execute custom JavaScript for data transformation

**Configuration Location:**
- Admin UI: Table menu > More > Webhooks
- Swagger UI: Available at `http://localhost:8080/api/v3/docs`

---

## 2. Planka API Documentation

### Authentication

**Access Token Endpoint:**
```
POST http://localhost:3000/api/access-tokens
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "emailOrUsername": "troy",
  "password": "planka-admin-2026"
}

Response:
{
  "item": {
    "accessToken": "your-token-here"
  }
}
```

**Using Token:**
```
Authorization: Bearer {accessToken}
```

All endpoints except `/api/access-tokens` require authorization.

### Core API Endpoints

**Reference:** https://github.com/plankanban/planka/blob/master/server/config/routes.js

#### Projects
```
GET    /api/projects
POST   /api/projects
GET    /api/projects/:id
PATCH  /api/projects/:id
DELETE /api/projects/:id
```

#### Boards
```
GET    /api/boards/:id
POST   /api/projects/:projectId/boards
PATCH  /api/boards/:id
DELETE /api/boards/:id
```

#### Lists (Columns)
```
POST   /api/boards/:boardId/lists
GET    /api/lists/:id
PATCH  /api/lists/:id
DELETE /api/lists/:id
POST   /api/lists/:id/move-cards  // Move cards between lists
```

#### Cards
```
POST   /api/lists/:listId/cards
GET    /api/cards/:id
PATCH  /api/cards/:id
DELETE /api/cards/:id
POST   /api/cards/:id/duplicate
```

**Card Creation Example:**
```json
POST /api/lists/:listId/cards
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {token}

{
  "name": "New Task",
  "description": "Task description",
  "position": 65535
}
```

**Card Update Example:**
```json
PATCH /api/cards/:cardId
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {token}

{
  "name": "Updated Title",
  "description": "New description",
  "position": 131071,
  "dueDate": "2026-02-15T00:00:00.000Z"
}
```

#### Card Memberships
```
POST   /api/cards/:cardId/memberships
DELETE /api/cards/:cardId/memberships/:userId
```

#### Labels
```
POST   /api/boards/:boardId/labels
PATCH  /api/labels/:id
DELETE /api/labels/:id
POST   /api/cards/:cardId/labels
DELETE /api/cards/:cardId/labels/:labelId
```

#### Tasks (Checklist Items)
```
POST   /api/cards/:cardId/tasks
PATCH  /api/tasks/:id
DELETE /api/tasks/:id
```

### Database Connection Details
- **Host:** planka-db (internal Docker network)
- **Database:** planka
- **User:** planka
- **Password:** planka-secret-password
- **Port:** 5432

---

## 3. n8n Workflow Patterns

### Pattern 1: NocoDB Record Change ‚Üí Planka Card Created

**Workflow File:** `/mnt/c/Users/password/Documents/.claude/docker/n8n-workflows/07-nocodb-to-planka-sync.json`

```json
{
  "name": "NocoDB to Planka Sync",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "nocodb-webhook",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "webhook-trigger",
      "name": "NocoDB Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [250, 300],
      "webhookId": "nocodb-insert"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const payload = $input.first().json;\nconst eventType = payload.type;\nconst records = payload.data.records || [];\n\n// Filter for insert events only\nif (eventType !== 'records.after.insert') {\n  return [];\n}\n\n// Transform NocoDB records to Planka card format\nreturn records.map(record => ({\n  json: {\n    cardName: record.Title || record.title || 'Untitled',\n    cardDescription: record.Description || record.description || '',\n    listId: '{{ $env.PLANKA_DEFAULT_LIST_ID }}',\n    position: 65535,\n    priority: record.Priority || record.priority || 'medium',\n    status: record.Status || record.status || 'pending',\n    nocodb_id: record.Id || record.id\n  }\n}));"
      },
      "id": "transform-data",
      "name": "Transform to Planka Format",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [450, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "http://planka:1337/api/access-tokens",
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "emailOrUsername",
              "value": "troy"
            },
            {
              "name": "password",
              "value": "planka-admin-2026"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "responseFormat": "json"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "get-planka-token",
      "name": "Get Planka Auth Token",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [650, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "=http://planka:1337/api/lists/{{ $json.listId }}/cards",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "=Bearer {{ $('Get Planka Auth Token').first().json.item.accessToken }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "name",
              "value": "={{ $json.cardName }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "description",
              "value": "={{ $json.cardDescription }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "position",
              "value": "={{ $json.position }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "responseFormat": "json"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "create-planka-card",
      "name": "Create Planka Card",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [850, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "json",
        "responseBody": "={{ { \"success\": true, \"planka_card_id\": $json.item.id, \"nocodb_id\": $('Transform to Planka Format').first().json.nocodb_id } }}"
      },
      "id": "response",
      "name": "Send Response",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [1050, 300]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "NocoDB Webhook": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Transform to Planka Format", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Transform to Planka Format": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Get Planka Auth Token", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Get Planka Auth Token": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Create Planka Card", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Create Planka Card": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Send Response", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    }
  },
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "tags": ["integration", "nocodb", "planka"]
}
```

**Setup Instructions:**
1. Deploy workflow to n8n
2. Copy webhook URL (e.g., `http://n8n:5678/webhook/nocodb-webhook`)
3. In NocoDB, create webhook:
   - Table menu > More > Webhooks > Create
   - Event: After Insert
   - URL: `http://n8n:5678/webhook/nocodb-webhook`
   - Method: POST

---

### Pattern 2: Planka Card Moved ‚Üí NocoDB Status Updated

**Workflow File:** `/mnt/c/Users/password/Documents/.claude/docker/n8n-workflows/08-planka-to-nocodb-sync.json`

```json
{
  "name": "Planka to NocoDB Status Sync",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "minutes",
              "minutesInterval": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "poll-trigger",
      "name": "Poll Every 2 Minutes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [250, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "http://planka:1337/api/access-tokens",
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "emailOrUsername",
              "value": "troy"
            },
            {
              "name": "password",
              "value": "planka-admin-2026"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "responseFormat": "json"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "auth-planka",
      "name": "Authenticate Planka",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [450, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "=http://planka:1337/api/boards/{{ $env.PLANKA_BOARD_ID }}",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "=Bearer {{ $json.item.accessToken }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "responseFormat": "json"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "get-board",
      "name": "Get Board with Cards",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [650, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const board = $input.first().json.item;\nconst lists = board.lists || [];\nconst cards = [];\n\n// Map list names to statuses\nconst statusMap = {\n  'To Do': 'pending',\n  'In Progress': 'in_progress',\n  'Done': 'completed',\n  'Backlog': 'backlog'\n};\n\nlists.forEach(list => {\n  const status = statusMap[list.name] || 'pending';\n  \n  (list.cards || []).forEach(card => {\n    // Only process cards updated in last 3 minutes\n    const updatedAt = new Date(card.updatedAt);\n    const threeMinutesAgo = new Date(Date.now() - 3 * 60 * 1000);\n    \n    if (updatedAt > threeMinutesAgo) {\n      cards.push({\n        json: {\n          card_id: card.id,\n          card_name: card.name,\n          list_name: list.name,\n          new_status: status,\n          description: card.description || ''\n        }\n      });\n    }\n  });\n});\n\nreturn cards;"
      },
      "id": "extract-cards",
      "name": "Extract Recently Updated Cards",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [850, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "=http://nocodb:8080/api/v3/{{ $env.NOCODB_PROJECT_ID }}/tables/{{ $env.NOCODB_TABLE_ID }}/records?where=(Title,eq,{{ $json.card_name }})",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "xc-token",
              "value": "={{ $env.NOCODB_API_TOKEN }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "responseFormat": "json"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "find-nocodb-record",
      "name": "Find NocoDB Record",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1050, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "url": "=http://nocodb:8080/api/v3/{{ $env.NOCODB_PROJECT_ID }}/tables/{{ $env.NOCODB_TABLE_ID }}/records/{{ $json.list[0].Id }}",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "xc-token",
              "value": "={{ $env.NOCODB_API_TOKEN }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Status",
              "value": "={{ $('Extract Recently Updated Cards').item.json.new_status }}"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "update-nocodb",
      "name": "Update NocoDB Status",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1250, 300],
      "continueOnFail": true
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Poll Every 2 Minutes": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Authenticate Planka", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Authenticate Planka": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Get Board with Cards", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Get Board with Cards": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Extract Recently Updated Cards", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Extract Recently Updated Cards": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Find NocoDB Record", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Find NocoDB Record": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Update NocoDB Status", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    }
  },
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "tags": ["integration", "planka", "nocodb", "sync"]
}
```

